headline: Williams-Sonoma, Inc. announces release date for third quarter results: Wednesday, November 19th, 2025
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, November 12, 2025--Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (NYSE: WSM) announced today that it will release its third quarter results on Wednesday, November 19th, 2025 before the market opens. Following the release via the wire services, the Company will host a conference call beginning at 10:00 AM Eastern Time, which can be accessed at http://ir.williams-sonomainc.com/events. Following the call, a replay of the webcast will be available at http://ir.williams-sonomainc.com/events beginning at 12:00
